/svg></span><span class=\"min-w-0 leading-tight\"><span class=\"block truncate font-editorial text-lg text-navy sm:text-xl\">Gönül İlhan</span><span class=\"block truncate text-[0.68rem] uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-muted-foreground sm:text-xs sm:tracking-[0.2em]\">Numeroloji</span></span></a><nav class=\"hidden items-center gap-1 lg:flex\" aria-label=\"Ana menü\"><a class=\"rounded-full px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-muted-foreground transition hover:bg-card hover:text-navy\" href=\"/\">Ana Sayfa</a><a class=\"rounded-full px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-muted-foreground transition hover:bg-card hover:text-navy\" href=\"/gonul-ilhan\">Gönül İlhan</a><a class=\"rounded-full px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-muted-foreground transition hover:bg-card hover:text-navy\" href=\"/hizmetler\">Hizmetler</a><a aria-current=\"page\" class=\"rounded-full px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium transition hover:bg-card hover:text-navy bg-card text-navy shadow-sm\" href=\"/egitimler\">Eğitimler</a><a class=\"rounded-full px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-muted-foreground transition hover:bg-card hover:text-navy\" href=\"/yorumlar\">Yorumlar</a><a class=\"rounded-full px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-muted-foreground transition hover:bg-card hover:text-navy\" href=\"/yazilar\">Yazılar</a><a class=\"rounded-full px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-muted-foreground transition hover:bg-card hover:text-navy\" href=\"/iletisim\">İletişim</a></nav><div class=\"hidden items-center gap-3 lg:flex\"><a class=\"inline-flex min-w-0 items-center justify-center gap-2 whitespace-normal rounded-full text-center text-sm font-medium leading-snug transition-all focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-ring focus-visible:ring-offset-2 disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 [&amp;&gt;svg]:shrink-0 bg-primary text-primary-foreground shadow-glow hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:bg-navy/92 min-h-9 px-4 py-2\" href=\"/randevu\">Randevu Al</a></div><button type=\"button\" class=\"inline-flex h-11 w-11 items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-border bg-card text-navy lg:hidden\" aria-label=\"Menüyü aç\" aria-expanded=\"false\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-menu h-5 w-5\"><line x1=\"4\" x2=\"20\" y1=\"12\" y2=\"12\"></line><line x1=\"4\" x2=\"20\" y1=\"6\" y2=\"6\"></line><line x1=\"4\" x2=\"20\" y1=\"18\" y2=\"18\"></line></svg></button></div></header><main><section class=\"container grid gap-10 py-14 sm:py-16 lg:grid-cols-[0.95fr_1.05fr] lg:items-end\"><div class=\"max-w-3xl space-y-4\"><span class=\"inline-flex max-w-full items-center whitespace-normal rounded-full border border-gold/30 bg-champagne/18 px-3 py-1 text-center text-xs font-medium leading-snug text-navy\">Eğitimler</span><h2 class=\"break-words font-editorial text-[2rem] leading-[1.1] text-navy sm:text-5xl sm:leading-[1.08]\">Numerolojiyi etik, anlaşılır ve uygulanabilir bir dille öğren.</h2><p class=\"text-base leading-7 text-muted-foreground sm:text-lg sm:leading-8\">Programlar; sayı arketiplerini tanımaktan harita okuma pratiğine kadar farklı seviyelerde katılım imkânı sunar.</p></div><div class=\"min-w-0 rounded-[1.5rem] border border-border/80 shadow-soft backdrop-blur bg-navy text-primary-foreground\"><div class=\"min-w-0 p-5 sm:p-6\"><p class=\"text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-champagne sm:text-sm sm:tracking-[0.2em]\">Eğitim yaklaşımı</p><p class=\"mt-4 text-base leading-8 text-primary-foreground/78\">Eğitimlerde amaç ezber değil, sembolik dili hayatla ilişkilendirme becerisidir. Her programda etik sınırlar, sade ifade ve kişisel farkındalık odağı korunur.</p></div></div></section><section class=\"container grid gap-5 pb-14 sm:pb-16 md:grid-cols-2\"><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(18px)\"><div class=\"min-w-0 rounded-[1.5rem] border border-border/80 bg-card/82 text-card-foreground shadow-soft backdrop-blur group flex h-full flex-col transition duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-rose/45\"><div class=\"min-w-0 space-y-2 p-5 sm:p-6\"><span class=\"inline-flex max-w-full items-center whitespace-normal rounded-full border border-gold/30 bg-champagne/18 px-3 py-1 text-center text-xs font-medium leading-snug text-navy w-fit\">Başlangıç</span><h3 class=\"break-words font-editorial text-2xl leading-tight text-navy\">Numerolojiye Giriş Eğitimi</h3></div><div class=\"min-w-0 p-5 pt-0 sm:p-6 sm:pt-0 flex flex-1 flex-col gap-5\"><p class=\"text-sm leading-7 text-muted-foreground\">Sayıların sembolik dilini öğrenmek ve kendi haritanı temel seviyede okumaya başlamak isteyenler için zarif bir başlangıç.</p><div class=\"grid gap-3 text-sm text-navy\"><span class=\"flex items-start gap-2\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-clock mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 shrink-0 text-gold\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><polyline points=\"12 6 12 12 16 14\"></polyline></svg>4 hafta</span><span class=\"flex items-start gap-2\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-monitor mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 shrink-0 text-gold\"><rect width=\"20\" height=\"14\" x=\"2\" y=\"3\" rx=\"2\"></rect><line x1=\"8\" x2=\"16\" y1=\"21\" y2=\"21\"></line><line x1=\"12\" x2=\"12\" y1=\"17\" y2=\"21\"></line></svg>Canlı online</span><span class=\"flex items-start gap-2\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-signal mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 shrink-0 text-gold\"><path d=\"M2 20h.01\"></path><path d=\"M7 20v-4\"></path><path d=\"M12 20v-8\"></path><path d=\"M17 20V8\"></path><path d=\"M22 4v16\"></path></svg>Numerolojiyle ilk kez tanışanlar, kişisel farkındalık çalışmalarına yeni bir araç eklemek isteyenler.</span></div><div class=\"mt-auto\"><a class=\"inline-flex min-w-0 items-center justify-center gap-2 whitespace-normal rounded-full text-center text-sm font-medium leading-snug transition-all focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-ring focus-visible:ring-offset-2 disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 [&amp;&gt;svg]:shrink-0 border border-border bg-card/70 text-foreground hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:border-gold/50 hover:bg-card min-h-11 px-6 py-2 w-full\" href=\"/egitimler/numerolojiye-giris-egitimi\">Eğitim Detaylarını Gör<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right h-4 w-4 transition group-hover:translate-x-1\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a></div></div></div></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(18px)\"><div class=\"min-w-0 rounded-[1.5rem] border border-border/80 bg-card/82 text-card-foreground shadow-soft backdrop-blur group flex h-full flex-col transition duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-rose/45\"><div class=\"min-w-0 space-y-2 p-5 sm:p-6\"><span class=\"inline-flex max-w-full items-center whitespace-normal rounded-full border border-gold/30 bg-champagne/18 px-3 py-1 text-center text-xs font-medium leading-snug text-navy w-fit\">İleri</span><h3 class=\"break-words font-editorial text-2xl leading-tight text-navy\">İleri Seviye Numeroloji Eğitimi</h3></div><div class=\"min-w-0 p-5 pt-0 sm:p-6 sm:pt-0 flex flex-1 flex-col gap-5\"><p class=\"text-sm leading-7 text-muted-foreground\">Temel bilgisi olan katılımcılar için yorumlama derinliği, harita sentezi ve danışmanlık dili odaklı program.</p><div class=\"grid gap-3 text-sm text-navy\"><span class=\"flex items-start gap-2\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-clock mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 shrink-0 text-gold\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><polyline points=\"12 6 12 12 16 14\"></polyline></svg>8 hafta</span><span class=\"flex items-start gap-2\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-monitor mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 shrink-0 text-gold\"><rect width=\"20\" height=\"14\" x=\"2\" y=\"3\" rx=\"2\"></rect><line x1=\"8\" x2=\"16\" y1=\"21\" y2=\"21\"></line><line x1=\"12\" x2=\"12\" y1=\"17\" y2=\"21\"></line></svg>Canlı online + uygulama</span><span class=\"flex items-start gap-2\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-signal mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 shrink-0 text-gold\"><path d=\"M2 20h.01\"></path><path d=\"M7 20v-4\"></path><path d=\"M12 20v-8\"></path><path d=\"M17 20V8\"></path><path d=\"M22 4v16\"></path></svg>Temel numeroloji bilgisine sahip, harita okuma becerisini derinleştirmek isteyen katılımcılar.</span></div><div class=\"mt-auto\"><a class=\"inline-flex min-w-0 items-center justify-center gap-2 whitespace-normal rounded-full text-center text-sm font-medium leading-snug transition-all focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-ring focus-visible:ring-offset-2 disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 [&amp;&gt;svg]:shrink-0 border border-border bg-card/70 text-foreground hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:border-gold/50 hover:bg-card min-h-11 px-6 py-2 w-full\" href=\"/egitimler/ileri-seviye-numeroloji-egitimi\">Eğitim Detaylarını Gör<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right h-4 w-4 transition group-hover:translate-x-1\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a></div></div></div></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(18px)\"><div class=\"min-w-0 rounded-[1.5rem] border border-border/80 bg-card/82 text-card-foreground shadow-soft backdrop-blur group flex h-full flex-col transition duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-rose/45\"><div class=\"min-w-0 space-y-2 p-5 sm:p-6\"><span class=\"inline-flex max-w-full items-center whitespace-normal rounded-full border border-gold/30 bg-champagne/18 px-3 py-1 text-center text-xs font-medium leading-snug text-navy w-fit\">Tüm seviyeler</span><h3 class=\"break-words font-editorial text-2xl leading-tight text-navy\">Kişisel Harita Okuma Atölyesi</h3></div><div class=\"min-w-0 p-5 pt-0 sm:p-6 sm:pt-0 flex flex-1 flex-col gap-5\"><p class=\"text-sm leading-7 text-muted-foreground\">Kendi doğum tarihi ve isim titreşimlerinle çalışarak haritanı rehber eşliğinde keşfedeceğin yoğun atölye.</p><div class=\"grid gap-3 text-sm text-navy\"><span class=\"flex items-start gap-2\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-clock mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 shrink-0 text-gold\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><polyline points=\"12 6 12 12 16 14\"></polyline></svg>1 gün</span><span class=\"flex items-start gap-2\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-monitor mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 shrink-0 text-gold\"><rect width=\"20\" height=\"14\" x=\"2\" y=\"3\" rx=\"2\"></rect><line x1=\"8\" x2=\"16\" y1=\"21\" y2=\"21\"></line><line x1=\"12\" x2=\"12\" y1=\"17\" y2=\"21\"></line></svg>Online veya yüz yüze</span><span class=\"flex items-start gap-2\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-signal mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 shrink-0 text-gold\"><path d=\"M2 20h.01\"></path><path d=\"M7 20v-4\"></path><path d=\"M12 20v-8\"></path><path d=\"M17 20V8\"></path><path d=\"M22 4v16\"></path></svg>Kendi haritası üzerinde çalışarak öğrenmek isteyen, deneyim odaklı katılımcılar.</span></div><div class=\"mt-auto\"><a class=\"inline-flex min-w-0 items-center justify-center gap-2 whitespace-normal rounded-full text-center text-sm font-medium leading-snug transition-all focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-ring focus-visible:ring-offset-2 disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 [&amp;&gt;svg]:shrink-0 border border-border bg-card/70 text-foreground hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:border-gold/50 hover:bg-card min-h-11 px-6 py-2 w-full\" href=\"/egitimler/kisisel-harita-okuma-atolyesi\">Eğitim Detaylarını Gör<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right h-4 w-4 transition group-hover:translate-x-1\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a></div></div></div></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(18px)\"><div class=\"min-w-0 rounded-[1.5rem] border border-border/80 bg-card/82 text-card-foreground shadow-soft backdrop-blur group flex h-full flex-col transition duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-rose/45\"><div class=\"min-w-0 space-y-2 p-5 sm:p-6\"><span class=\"inline-flex max-w-full items-center whitespace-normal rounded-full border border-gold/30 bg-champagne/18 px-3 py-1 text-center text-xs font-medium leading-snug text-navy w-fit\">Orta / İleri</span><h3 class=\"break-words font-editorial text-2xl leading-tight text-navy\">Uygulamalı Numeroloji Programı</h3></div><div class=\"min-w-0 p-5 pt-0 sm:p-6 sm:pt-0 flex flex-1 flex-col gap-5\"><p class=\"text-sm leading-7 text-muted-foreground\">Harita okuma pratiğini artırmak, soru-cevap alanı açmak ve danışmanlık becerisini geliştirmek isteyenler için uygulama programı.</p><div class=\"grid gap-3 text-sm text-navy\"><span class=\"flex items-start gap-2\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-clock mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 shrink-0 text-gold\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><polyline points=\"12 6 12 12 16 14\"></polyline></svg>6 hafta</span><span class=\"flex items-start gap-2\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-monitor mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 shrink-0 text-gold\"><rect width=\"20\" height=\"14\" x=\"2\" y=\"3\" rx=\"2\"></rect><line x1=\"8\" x2=\"16\" y1=\"21\" y2=\"21\"></line><line x1=\"12\" x2=\"12\" y1=\"17\" y2=\"21\"></line></svg>Küçük grup</span><span class=\"flex items-start gap-2\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-signal mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 shrink-0 text-gold\"><path d=\"M2 20h.01\"></path><path d=\"M7 20v-4\"></path><path d=\"M12 20v-8\"></path><path d=\"M17 20V8\"></path><path d=\"M22 4v16\"></path></svg>Numerolojiyi öğrenmiş fakat daha fazla pratik, geri bildirim ve yorumlama özgüveni isteyenler.</span></div><div class=\"mt-auto\"><a class=\"inline-flex min-w-0 items-center justify-center gap-2 whitespace-normal rounded-full text-center text-sm font-medium leading-snug transition-all focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-ring focus-visible:ring-offset-2 disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 [&amp;&gt;svg]:shrink-0 border border-border bg-card/70 text-foreground hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:border-gold/50 hover:bg-card min-h-11 px-6 py-2 w-full\" href=\"/egitimler/uygulamali-numeroloji-programi\">Eğitim Detaylarını Gör<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right h-4 w-4 transition group-hover:translate-x-1\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"container py-14 sm:py-16\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(18px)\"><div class=\"sacred-frame overflow-hidden rounded-[2rem] bg-navy-depth p-5 text-primary-foreground shadow-soft min-[390px]:p-6 sm:p-12 lg:p-14\"><div class=\"grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-[1fr_auto] lg:items-center\"><div class=\"max-w-2xl space-y-4\"><p class=\"text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-champagne sm:text-sm sm:tracking-[0.24em]\">Nazik bir başlangıç</p><h2 class=\"break-words font-editorial text-[2rem] leading-tight sm:text-5xl\">Hangi eğitim sana uygun, birlikte netleştirelim.</h2><p class=\"text-base leading-8 text-primary-foreground/76\">Eğitim seviyenden emin değilsen kısa bir ön görüşme ile ihtiyacına 